column5: Nice fish man! Would be nice to get out soon.
You just backed right in over that snow drift eh? LOL Thought I seen James truck at the launch.  Nice one dude.

Brian,  wasn't too bad actually....and all was melting on the way back. Also others did it ahead of me. We all had shovels, but I didn't sense much desire to use them first thing in the morning  Cheers, Ice Fisherman
I brought shovels... but we said screw it. Might be back in the am
Awesome that you guys are boating in January!  I guess you dont winterize your boat? Run it all year if possible?
Awesome, with I lived closer still
